columnDefinitions.headerName:
[Zp,q]
For wells without plunger lifts, if HRp,q is less than 1, then Zp,q is equal to 0;
if HRp,q is greater than or equal to 1, then Zp,q is equal to 1

For wells with plunger lifts, if HRp,q is less than 0.5, then Zp,q is equal to 0;
if HRp,q is greater than or equal to 0.5, then Zp,q is equal to 1
